15:34.980 --> 15:36.300
But that started to shift.

15:36.300 --> 15:38.220
Almost, if you look at the history of things,

15:38.220 --> 15:39.700
and we have some links in the show notes,

15:39.700 --> 15:43.540
about six months after Wayland's release,

15:43.540 --> 15:45.020
everything kind of shifts.

15:45.020 --> 15:47.860
